<span style="font-weight: 400;">According to her, the main cause of Atrial fibrillation is: </span><b>Lack of joy, dealing with issues from anger. Not love.¬†</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the ways of doing this is through saying or writing affirmations. Her affirmation for healing Atrial fibrillation is: </span><b>My heart beats to the rhythm of love</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">.¬†</span>";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"0";}}